attributes.Long form description: The student starts by attaching the joycon controllers to the Nintendo Switch, then detaching them, attaching them to the joycon straps, detaching them again, and placing them on the Comfort grip, then placing the Nintendo Switch on the kickstand, then exchanging the game card for a new one, doing the same with the SD card, and finally turning the Nintendo Switch off and on.
